    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "From https://github.com/dotnet/platform-compat/blob/master/docs/DE0005.md:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/47029823/200192839-61c03b9d-b368-4c94-bdd1-d4071e3d700b.png)\r\n\r\nThat's exactly what I need it for. Email me a small report once a day. One email per day. Does not need to scale, I don't want to compete with Mailchimp.\r\n\r\nThe problem is that its EHLO logic does not adhere to RFC and some mail services drop the connection as a result.\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://opengraph.githubassets.com/c04b6ad0c4764cfe0c61548173a68495a115b0e2aa00e7e54f4ec19ce7470d42/dotnet/platform-compat\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><img src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/favicons/favicon.svg\" height=\"14\"> GitHub</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/dotnet/platform-compat\">platform-compat/DE0005.md at master · dotnet/platform-compat</a></strong></div><div>Roslyn analyzer that finds usages of APIs that will throw PlatformNotSupportedException on certain platforms. - platform-compat/DE0005.md at master · dotnet/platform-compat</div></blockquote>",
